rComments: Do the work get an A, very simple.  You have multiple chances to make up assignments that you screw up and there is a lot of extra credit.  Nearly everyone gets an A.  Highly recommend!
Prof. Zinnes is an amazing instructor and on top of that she's kind, smart, and really takes an interest in her students! I highly recommend taking a class with her!
Gave a lot of extra credit...and more than 90% of the class gets an A+!
